"To establish, implement, manage, and improve the provision of technical expertise for all project information disciplines throughout Network Rail Wales and Western Programmes of work; with the purpose of ensuring that project and programme project information deliverables and activities can deliver effective and efficient procurement, production, delivery and transfer of project information to meet business standards and relevant legislation. To support Wales and Western and wider business in the development of technical and technological solutions and strategies that improves or enhances the methodologies and working practices for managing project information."